"Camp Keeley"...

1246
01:26:09,437 --> 01:26:10,927
Onde estão indo?

1247
01:26:12,606 --> 01:26:14,438
South Beach, Flórida.

1248
01:26:15,945 --> 01:26:17,206
Onde conseguimos isso?

1249
01:26:17,447 --> 01:26:20,609
